    <div class="content-container">
      
      <div class="content">
        
        <h2 class="add-top-margin">Ótú ésì ètínyé òkè ń'ásụ̀sụ́ Ìgbò  nà Common Voice</h2>
        <hr>
       <p>Ị́ nwèrè íké ítụ̄nyē  òkè  n'ásụ̀sụ́  Ìgbò n'ụ́zọ̀ ńdị́ à:</p>
       <ul>
        <li><span class='custom-button-danger howHelp'>Kpọ̀nyé ólú gị́</span> </li>
        <li> <span class='custom-button-info howHelp'>Kwàdó ḿkpọ́nyé ńdị́ ọ̀zọ́</span>. </li>
       </ul> 
       <strong>Ụ̀fọ́dụ́ íhé ị́ kwèsị̀rị̀ ímā:</strong>
     <ul>
       <li>Bíkō gụ̀ọ́ íhé <a href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/ig/privacy" target="blank">Common Voice Privacy policy</a> Bíkō gụ̀ọ́ íhé kà Í ghọ́tá íhé éjì data gí èmé.</li>
       <li>Túpú Ì kpọ́nyé ólū, ị́ nwèrè íké ị́mēpụ̀tà profaịlụ gí  <a href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/login" target="blank">ébé à</a>. Ǹké à ábụ̄ghị̄ ìwú, mànà ọ́ gà ènyéré ányí áká ị́chīkọ́tá ǹjìrìmárá ónyé màkà<a href="fame.html">Hall of Fame ànyí</a>.</li>
     </ul>
        <p class="text">
          <img class="image no-top-margin center add-top-margin-small" src="../img/homepage.PNG">
        </p>
       
        <div class="custom-tab" id="custom-tab">
          <div class="custom-tab-menu center">
            <a class="custom-tab-menu-item active" data-content="image">Òtù Í gà-èsí kpọ̀nyé ólú gị́</a>
            <a class="custom-tab-menu-item" data-content="table">Òtù Í gà-èsí kwàdó ḿkpọ́nyé ńdị́ ọ̀zọ́</a>
          </div>
          <div class="custom-tab-content" data-content="image">
            <h3>Òtù Í gà-èsí kpọ̀nyé ólú gị́</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Íbūrū ụ́zọ̀ kpọ̀nyé ólú gị́ pia <a href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/ig/speak" target="blank"><button class="recordBtnClick custom-button custom-button-danger pulse-danger">Kwùó ókwú</button></a>
              </li>
              <li>Kà browsa a sèté ólú gī pìá kpọ̀wányé  (<img class="recordBtn image no-top-margin max-width-200 center add-top-margin-small" src="../img/recordBtn.PNG">) bìdózíé íkwū ókwú.
                <li>Pị̀á kwụ̀sị́ (<img class="recordBtn image no-top-margin max-width-200 center add-top-margin-small" src="../img/stopBtn.PNG">) kà ḿkpọ́nyé kwụ́sị́.</li> 
                </li>
             <li>Ị́kwèsị̀rị̀ ị́kpọ̄nyē <strong>5</strong> ḿkpọ́nyé túpú ị̀ nyéfèé yā.</li>
             <li>Pìá <mark>Nyéfèé</mark> ị́nyēfē ḿkpọ́nyé gị̄.</li>
            </ol>
            <h4> Bíkō gụ̀ọ́ mà  ghọ̀tá íhé </h4>
            <hr>
            <ul>
              <li>Bíkō chọ̀ọ́ ébé ḿkpọ́tụ́ ná-ádị̄ghī.</li>
              <li> Ọ́ bụ́rụ́ nà Í gà ènwé íké bíkō jìrí earphone wèré kpọ́nyé ólū gī. Ǹké à gà-èmé kà ó sèté ólū gī ǹkè ómá. </li>
                <li> Ọ́búrú nà Í chọ́pụ̀tá nà Ì máchāghị̄ òtù Í gà-èsí kpọ́pụ̀tà ahíríókwū ọ́bụ́là, Í nwèrè íké ímāfè yá. </li>

            </ul>
          
           <!-- <p class="text text-center graph-title">Then Go to Step 2</p>-->
           
          </div>
          <div class="custom-tab-content" data-content="table">
            <h3>Ọ́bụ́rụ́ nà ị́chọ̀rọ̀ íkwàdò ḿkpọ́nyé</h3>
            <ol>
              <li>Bíkō gụ̀ọ́ mà  ghọ̀tá íhé <a href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/ig/criteria" target="blank"><strong>validation criteria</strong></a> before you start validating.</li>
                
              <li>Ọ́bụ́rụ́ nà ị́chọ̀rọ̀ íkwàdò, bùrú úzọ̀ pìá <a href="https://commonvoice.mozilla.org/ig/listen" target="blank"><button class="recordBtnClick custom-button custom-button-info pulse-info">Gèé ńtị̀</button></a>
              </li>
              <li>Pị̀á kpọ̀ọ́ (<img class="recordBtn image" src="../img/playBtn.PNG">) kà Í gèé ḿkpọ́nyé.
                <li>Ọ́bụ́rụ́ nà Í gècháá, pìá <img class="approveBtn recordBtn" src="../img/approveBtn.PNG"> kà íkwàdó ḿkpọ́nyé áhụ̀ màọ̀bụ́ <img class="recordBtn image no-top-margin max-width-200 center add-top-margin-small" src="../img/rejectBtn.PNG"> kà Í jụ́ ḿkpọ́nyé áhụ̀.</li>
                <li>Ọ́búrú nà Í chọ́pụ̀tá nà Ì máchāghị̄ mà ọ̀ dì ḿmā màọ̀bụ̀ nà òdị́ghị́ ḿmā, pìá <mark>Máfèé</mark> kà Ị́ máfèé ńkwàdó ḿkpọ́nyé áhụ̀. </li>
                </ol>
          
           <!-- <img class="image no-top-margin center add-top-margin-small" src="img/speak.PNG">-->
         
          </div>
        
        </div>
      
        <div class="content-table flex-column">
